# Cloudflare Pages _redirects for rald.cloud
# Note: /api/* routes are handled by the rald-cloud-edge CF Worker (rald.cloud/api/*),
# so Worker traffic never reaches Pages. Only the SPA catch-all is needed here.

# SPA catch-all — serve index.html for all non-asset client-side routes.
# Required for deep-links: /payrald, /loop, /dispatch, /voice, /legal/*, etc.
# Must be last — Cloudflare Pages matches rules top-to-bottom.
/*  /index.html  200
